====Introduction to IHMC CMAP Tools====
The Institute for Human and Machine Computing produced "Concept Mapping Tools" (CMAP Tools) to aid a world-wide network of collaborators in the task of producing multi-media documents that allowed users to define relationships between documents and edit them live on the internet.

====Get CMAP Tools====
You can download a copy of CMAP Tools for your personal use from the website at http://cmap.ihmc.us/.  The link to download is http://cmap.ihmc.us/download/.

====Advantages of CMAP Tools====
Here are some of the advantages of CMAP Tools:

*Unlimited concepts in a map, and all concepts can link to each other
*Several supported operating systems
*Live, free collaboration online
*Formatted output can be re-used by a number of other programs and services


